{
  "stem": "14168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they had a Jew, and they said these are the inferior races.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We Jews had to be there, and listen to all that nonsense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, anyway, back to what we were discussing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In 1936, the Nazis relented a little bit because, at that time, we had the Olympiad-- the Olympic games in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Hitler had invited everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And for a time-- but at least for a-- a few months-- Germany became a Potemkin village, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everything was disguised.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everybody was welcome, of course, except Joe Lewis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't think Hitler shook hands with him at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then it started again in 1937.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Nazis had, in the meantime, set up concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "First, they had only-- they got the-- their opponents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They-- they sent their opponents to concentration camps and Jews who had been prominent in-- as members of the democratic parties-- democratic movement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then they tried to also cut the Jews off from economic activities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They brought pressure on people, like my dad, too-- they brought pressure on people-- to-- to Jews to sell their business enterprises.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if they didn't want to, other means [BACKROUND NOISE] were employed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They, of course, the sale was nothing but a sham.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now, in 1938--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- my father was a sales representative, so he-- he actually lived off of his commission.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the Nazis already made it very unpleasant for Jews to visit non-Jewish business places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Jews were not allowed, for instance, certain places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In restaurants, there were big signs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, in certain parks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were just treated like, I would say-- sometimes I would say worse than animals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I formed the idea I want to get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
